Product description

Size:3 Ounce

Coppertone Waterbabies is the #1 pediatrician recommended sunscreen brand. It is strong protection from the sun's most harmful rays, yet gentle enough for baby's delicate skin. Coppertone Waterbabies sunscreen is broad spectrum UVA/UVB protection, it's water-resistant, and hypoallergenic.
